19:["$","p","p-8",{"children":"The Amazon Basics 7-in-1 ran hot (44°C average) and caused display flicker on the Windows laptop during video calls. The Satechi Slim's 30Hz display output is a dealbreaker for anything beyond a second document reference screen."}]
